## Form Inputs (CONSISTENT STYLING)

### Text Input
```typescript
<div>
  <label className={`block text-sm font-medium mb-1 ${isDark ? 'text-dark-300' : 'text-gray-700'}`}>
    Label <span className="text-red-500">*</span>
  </label>
  <input
    type="text"
    value={value}
    onChange={(e) => setValue(e.target.value)}
    className={`w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border transition-colors
      ${isDark 
        ? 'bg-dark-700 border-dark-600 text-white placeholder-dark-400' 
        : 'bg-white border-gray-300 text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-400'
      } focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500/20 focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none`}
    placeholder="Placeholder text"
  />
</div>
```

